# Mosquitto ACL — CEROS / ROS2-RCS Twin (F2 data pipeline)
#
# F2 keeps it simple: a single `ceros` user with full read/write on the
# entire `ceros/#` tree, plus a `health` user used only by the
# healthcheck for read access to $SYS.
#
# Granular per-role ACL (operator vs rover vs autopilot, separate certs)
# is F10 hardening. See INTERFACE_CONTRACT.md §3.
#
# Reload after editing: docker compose restart mosquitto

# Healthcheck (internal use only)
user health
topic read $SYS/#

# Main CEROS user — used by both the Jetson bridge and the operator frontend
user ceros
topic readwrite ceros/#
